  "title": "IT ENGINEER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Provide user support and maintenance for company systems and devices.</li><li>Monitor and maintain system security, including email protection and access controls.</li><li>Install, configure, and update software applications as needed.</li><li>Implement and manage data backup and recovery solutions.</li><li>Troubleshoot hardware and software issues promptly to minimize downtime.</li><li>Ensure compliance with IT policies and best practices.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma/Degree in Information Technology, Computer Science, or related field.</li><li>Proven experience in IT support and system administration.</li><li>Strong knowledge of network security, email and server systems and security, and backup solutions.</li><li>Excellent problem-solving skills and attention to detail.</li><li>Ability to work independently</li></ul>",
